<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Book Notes</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Rahul Joy's - Book Notes</h1>
        <p class="book-meta">A personal collection of notes, takeaways & reflections from books Iâ€™ve read.</p>
    </section>
    <hr class="section-divider">
